headline.main: PROSECUTOR CONFERS ON PARK AVE. CANTEEN; Questions Promoter and Women Workers for Project

lead_paragraph: Assistant District Attorney Herman Stichman began an investigation yesterday into the Park Avenue Canteen, which it had been proposed to locate in the former home of the late Charles R. Steele at 11 East Sixty-second Street, with the examination of several witnesses.
abstract: promoter, G L Fecke, being investigated
